  "title": "M&E Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate and management of all M&amp;E works</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the supervision and coordination of M&amp;E works at project site</li>\n  <li>Ensure all M&amp;E works are performed on time, within budget and in compliance with all necessary standards, code of practice and safety regulations</li>\n  <li>General on-site technical &amp; engineering matters and quality checks</li>\n  <li>Monitor progress, quality of workmanship and compliance with requirements</li>\n  <li>Review and align M&amp;E design and project drawings to ensure compliance with specification and guidelines</li>\n  <li>Review project specifications and technical clarifications</li>\n  <li>Prepare structural penetration shop-drawing for approval</li>\n  <li>Prepare M&amp;E coordination drawings and liaise with Architectural Coordinators and Design Engineers to issue drawing for approval</li>\n  <li>To produce M&amp;E Coordination drawing.</li>\n  <li>Maintain M&amp;E drawing records.</li>\n  <li>Attend site meeting and technical meeting with Consultants</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Engineering, Civil Engineering or relevant field</li>\n  <li>Experienced for M&amp;E works such as ACMV, Electrical, Plumbing and Sanitary etc</li>\n  <li>Must have main contractor experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com</strong></a><strong> </strong>or call <a href=\"tel:+(65) 6220 0847\"><strong>+(65) 6220 0847</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd<br>\nEA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
